
rāh-e-dūr-e-ishq meñ rotā hai kyā 
aage aage dekhiye hotā hai kyā 
qāfile meñ sub.h ke ik shor hai 
ya.anī ġhāfil ham chale sotā hai kyā 
sabz hotī hī nahīñ ye sarzamīñ 
tuḳhm-e-ḳhvāhish dil meñ tū botā hai kyā 
ye nishān-e-ishq haiñ jaate nahīñ 
daaġh chhātī ke abas dhotā hai kyā 
ġhairat-e-yūsuf hai ye vaqt-e-azīz 
'mīr' us ko rā.egāñ khotā hai kyā 